<head> 

    <link rel="icon" href="~/images/favicon.png" type="image/x-icon" />
    <title>Iletisim - Kerim Berkay Buçan</title>

    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:400,100,300,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <link href="~/css/contactstyle.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/css/docs.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="~/js/contactpage.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/email-decode.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/popper.js"></script>

</head>
<body>
    <section class="ftco-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-md-6 text-center mb-5">
                    <h2 class="heading-section">İletişim Sayfası</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <div class="wrapper">
                        <div class="row mb-5">
                            <div class="col-md-3">
                                <div class="dbox w-100 text-center">
                                    <div class="icon d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                        <span class="fa fa-map-marker"></span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text">
                                        <p><span>Adres:</span> Yeni Mahalle Şehit Astsubay Mustafa Soner Varlık Caddesi No:77, 10200 Bandırma/Balıkesir</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-3">
                                <div class="dbox w-100 text-center text-yellow">
                                    <div class="icon d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                        <span class="fa fa-phone"></span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text">
                                        <p><span>Telefon:</span> <a href="tel://905395535895">+90 539 553 58 95</a></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-3">
                                <div class="dbox w-100 text-center">
                                    <div class="icon d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                        <span class="fa fa-paper-plane"></span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text">
                                        <p><span>Email:</span> <a href="mailto:kerim@berkay.org.tr"><span>kerim@berkay.org.tr</span></a></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-3">
                                <div class="dbox w-100 text-center">
                                    <div class="icon d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                        <span class="fa fa-globe"></span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text">
                                        <p><span>Website</span> <a href="#">berkay.org.tr</a></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="row no-gutters ">
                            <div class="col-md-7">
                                <div class="contact-wrap w-100 p-md-5 p-4" style="background-color: #f8f0d2;">
                                    <h3 class="mb-4">İletişim Formu</h3>

                                    <div id="form-message-warning" class="mb-4"></div>
                                    <div id="form-message-success" class="mb-4">
                                        Mesajınız İletildi, en yakın zamanda iletişime geçilecektir.
                                    </div>
                                    <form asp-action="Index" method="POST" id="contactForm" name="contactForm" class="contactForm">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <label class="label" for="name">Ad Soyad</label>
                                                    <input type="text" class="form-control rounded-pill p-2 text-center" name="AdSoyad" id="name" placeholder="Kerim Berkay Buçan" maxlength="150" minlength="3" required>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <label class="label" for="email">Mail Adresi</label>
                                                    <input type="email" class="form-control rounded-pill p-2 text-center" name="MailAdres" id="email" placeholder="kerim@berkay.org.tr" maxlength="150" minlength="10" required>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-12">
                                            <div class="form-group">
                                                <label class="label" for="phone">Telefon Numarası</label>
                                                <div>
                                                    <input type="tel" class="form-control rounded-pill p-2 text-center" name="TelefonNumarasi" id="phone" placeholder="905395535895" maxlength="150" minlength="6"  required>
                                                </div>


                                            </div>
                                        </div>


                                        <div class="col-md-12">
                                            <div class="form-group">
                                                <label class="label" for="subject">Konu</label>

                                                <select class="form-control rounded-pill text-center p-2" id="subject" name="Konu" required>
                                                    <option>Lütfen konu seçiniz.</option>
                                                    <option>Web Tasarım - Web Geliştirme</option>
                                                    <option>Mobil Uygulama Geliştirme</option>
                                                    <option>Logo Tasarımı - Sosyal Medya Yönetimi</option>
                                                    <option>Domain Hizmetleri</option>
                                                    <option>Marka Tescili ve Yönetimi</option>
                                                </select>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                        <div class="col-md-12">
                                            <div class="form-group">
                                                <label class="label" for="message">Mesajınız</label>
<textarea name="Mesaj" class="form-control  p-3 " id="message" cols="30" rows="4" placeholder="Projemi sizinli birlikte yürütmek istiyorum...." maxlength="150" minlength="5"  required></textarea>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="">
                                        </div>

                                        <div>
                                        </div>

                                        <div class="col-md-12">
                                            <div class="form-group">
                                                <label class="label" for="message">Proje Bütçesi</label>
                                                <div class="input-group flex-nowrap">
                                                    <span class="input-group-text" id="addon-wrapping">$</span>
                                                    <input name="ProjeButcesi" type="text" class="form-control p-3 text-center" placeholder="X.XXX - XXX.XXX" maxlength="150" minlength="2" required>
                                                </div>



                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                                <div class="form-group text-center">
                                                    <input type="submit" value="İletişime Geç" class="btn btn-warning text-center">
                                                    <div class="submitting"></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="text-center">
                                                <a asp-controller="Anasayfa" asp-action="Index"><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm">Anasayfaya Dön</button></a>
                                            </div>

                                        </div>

                                    </form>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-5 d-flex align-items-stretch">
                                <div class="info-wrap w-100 p-5 img" style="background-image: url();">
                                    <img class="img-fluid mb-4" src="~/images/sari.png">
                                    <p>
                                        Dijital bütün işlerinizde bizimle iletişime geçebilirsiniz ! Web Tasarım, Logo Tasarım, Mobil Uygulama Geliştirme,Sosyal Medya Yönetimi, Domain Hizmetleri , Marka Yönetimi.

                                    </p>

                                    <div id="carouselExampleFade" class="carousel slide carousel-fade" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                                        <div class="carousel-inner">
                                            <div class="carousel-item active">
                                                <img src="~/images/webtasarim.jpg" class="img-fluid">

                                            </div>
                                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                                <img src="~/images/mobiluygulama.jpg" class="img-fluid">
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                                <img src="~/images/marka-tescil.jpg" class="img-fluid">

                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleFade" data-bs-slide="prev">
                                            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>

                                        </button>
                                        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleFade" data-bs-slide="next">
                                            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>

                                        </button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="m-5"></div>
    </section>
</body>